pageContext.claim: “Rudy Giuliani was seeking out corruption, and what happens mostly in the 2016 election, because there was tremendous corruption in the 2016 election.”
pageContext.analysis: It's unclear what Trump means by "corruption in the 2016 election." Russia intervened in that election, according to U.S. intelligence and the special counsel's report, and Giuliani has tried to promote an unfounded theory that Ukraine intervened in the 2016 election.
